ldering fire was in his eyes.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9015','2016-03-12 15:22:11','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(150,10,3,1,31,'04031','Rivendell Blade','Item. Weapon.','Attach to a <b><i>Noldor</i></b> or <b><i>Silvan</i></b> character. Restricted.\nWhen attached character attacks an enemy, that enemy gets -2 [defense] until the end of the phase.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9023','2016-03-12 15:22:12','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(151,10,4,1,32,'04032','Hail of Stones','','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust X characters to deal X damage to an enemy in the staging area.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9014','2016-03-12 15:22:12','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(152,10,2,2,33,'04033','Rider of the Mark','Rohan.','<b>Action:</b> Spend 1 [spirit] resource to give control of Rider of the Mark to another player. (Limit once per round.)\n<b>Response:</b> After Rider of the Mark changes control, discard a shadow card dealt to an enemy you are engaged with.','',0,'3',NULL,2,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9022','2016-03-12 15:22:13','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(153,10,3,2,34,'04034','Song of Eärendil','Song.','Attach to a [spirit] hero.\n<b>Response:</b> After Song of Eärendil enters play, draw 1 card.\n<b>Response:</b> After another player raises his threat, raise your threat by 1 to reduce that player\'s threat by 1.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9026','2016-03-12 15:26:22','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(154,10,2,4,35,'04035','Bombur','Dwarf.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Bombur to choose a location. That location gets -1 [threat] until the end of the phase. (That location does not contribute its [threat] instead if it is an <b><i>Underground</i></b> location.)',NULL,1,'3',NULL,0,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9007','2016-03-12 15:26:27','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(155,10,4,4,36,'04036','Out of the Wild','','Secrecy 2.\n<b>Action:</b> Search the top 5 cards of the encounter deck for any 1 non-objective card worth no victory points and add it to your victory display. Shuffle the encounter deck.','',0,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9020','2016-03-12 15:26:30','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(156,10,4,5,37,'04037','The End Comes','','<b>Response:</b> After a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> character leaves play, shuffle the encounter discard pile back into the encounter deck.','\'He is dead then,\', said Frodo. \'I feared it was so.\'\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801209c9027','2016-03-12 15:26:33','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(157,11,1,4,53,'04053','Aragorn','Dúnedain. Ranger.','Sentinel.\n<b>Refresh Action:</b> Reduce your threat to your starting threat level. (Limit once per game.)','\"I am older than I look, I might prove useful.\"\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,12,2,3,2,5,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9001','2016-03-12 15:28:27','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(158,11,4,3,54,'04054','Grave Cairn','','<b>Response:</b> After a character leaves play, add its [attack] to another character\'s [attack] until the end of the round.','\"We have not the time or the tools to bury our comrade fitly, or to raise a mound up over him. A cairn we might build.\"\n<cite>Legolas, The Two Towers</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9007','2016-03-12 15:28:28','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(159,11,3,3,55,'04055','Sword that was Broken','Artifact.','Attach to a hero.\r\nAttached hero gains a [leadership] resource icon.\r\nIf attached hero is Aragorn, each character you control gets +1 [willpower].','\"For the Sword that was Broken is the Sword of Elendil that broke beneath him when he fell.\"\r\n<cite>Aragorn, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9018','2016-03-12 15:28:28','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(160,11,2,1,56,'04056','Watcher of the Bruinen','Noldor. Warrior.','Sentinel.\nWatcher of the Bruinen does not exhaust to defend.\n<b>Forced:</b> After Watcher of the Bruinen defends, either discard it from play or discard 1 card from your hand.','',0,'2',NULL,0,1,2,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9025','2016-03-12 15:28:29','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(161,11,3,1,57,'04057','Rivendell Bow','Item. Weapon.','Attach to a <b><i>Noldor</i></b> or <b><i>Silvan</i></b> character, or to Aragorn. Limit 1 per character.\r\nAttached character gains ranged.\r\nIf attached character has the printed ranged keyword, it gets +1 [attack] during a ranged attack.',NULL,0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9013','2016-03-12 15:28:29','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(162,11,2,2,58,'04058','Arwen Undómiel','Noldor. Noble.','<b>Response:</b> After Arwen Undómiel exhausts, choose a character. That character gains sentinel and gets +1 [defense] until the end of the round.','...in whom it was said that the likeness of Lúthien had come on earth again...for she was the Evenstar of her people.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,2,0,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9002','2016-03-12 15:28:30','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(163,11,4,2,59,'04059','Elrond\'s Counsel','','<b>Action:</b> If you control a unique <b><i>Noldor</i></b> character, give another character +1 [willpower] until the end of the phase and lower your threat by 3.','\"Believe rather that it is so ordered that we, who sit here, and none others, must now find counsel for the peril of the world.\"\n<cite>Elrond, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9005','2016-03-12 15:28:30','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(164,11,4,4,60,'04060','Short Cut',NULL,'<b>Response:</b> After a location enters play, exhaust a <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> character to shuffle that location back into the encounter deck. Then, reveal 1 card from the encounter deck and add it to the staging area.','\"I suppose we haven\'t lost more than two days by my short cut through the Forest!\"\r\n<cite>Frodo, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9014','2016-03-12 15:28:31','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(165,11,3,4,61,'04061','Legacy of Durin','Condition.','Attach to a Dwarf hero.\n<b>Response:</b> After you play a Dwarf character from your hand, draw 1 card.','',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9009','2016-03-12 15:28:31','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(166,11,3,5,62,'04062','Resourceful','','Secrecy 3.\nAttach to a hero you control.\nAttached hero collects 1 additional resource during the resource phase each round.','',0,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801210c9012','2016-03-12 15:28:32','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(167,12,1,1,76,'04076','Háma','Rohan. Warrior.','<b>Response:</b> After Háma is declared as an attacker, return a [tactics] event from your discard pile to your hand. Then, choose and discard 1 card from your hand.','\"Yet in doubt a man of worth will trust to his own wisdom.\" <cite>The Two Towers</cite>',1,NULL,9,1,3,1,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9016','2016-03-12 15:32:31','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(168,12,2,3,77,'04077','Erestor','Noldor.','<b>Action:</b> Choose and discard 1 card from your hand to draw 1 card. (Limit once per round.)','Beside Glorfindel there were several other counsellors of Elrond\'s household, of whom Erestor was the chief...\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'4',NULL,2,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9008','2016-03-12 15:32:32','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(169,12,4,3,78,'04078','Fresh Tracks','','<b>Response:</b> After an enemy is added to the staging area, deal 1 damage to that enemy. Players ignore that enemy while making engagement checks this round.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9012','2016-03-12 15:32:32','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(170,12,2,1,79,'04079','Erebor Battle Master','Dwarf. Warrior.','Erebor Battle Master gets +1 [attack] for each other <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> ally you control.',NULL,0,'3',NULL,0,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9007','2016-03-12 15:32:33','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(171,12,3,1,80,'04080','Ring Mail','Item. Armor.','Attach to a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> or <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> character. Restricted.\nAttached character gets +1 hit point and +1 [defense].','\"And all the arrows of all the hunters in the world would be in vain...\"\n<cite>Gimli, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9021','2016-03-12 15:32:33','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(172,12,4,2,81,'04081','Out of Sight','','Secrecy 3.\n<b>Action:</b> Enemies engaged with you cannot attack you this phase.','',0,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9020','2016-03-12 15:32:34','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(173,12,3,2,82,'04082','Ever My Heart Rises','Condition.','Attach a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> character.\r\n<b>Response:</b> After you travel to a <b><i>Mountain</i></b> or <b><i>Underground</i></b> location, ready attached character and reduce your threat by 1.','\'This is more to my liking,\' said the dwarf, stomping on the stones. \'Ever my heart rises as we draw near the mountains.\'\r\n<cite>The Two Towers</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9009','2016-03-12 15:32:34','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(174,12,2,4,83,'04083','Warden of Healing','Gondor. Healer.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Warden of Healing to heal 1 damage on up to 2 different characters. Then, you may pay 2 [lore] resources to ready Warden of Healing.','\"But for long years we healers have only sought to patch the rents made by the men of swords.\" <cite>Return of the King</cite>',0,'2',NULL,1,0,1,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9026','2016-03-12 15:32:35','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(175,12,4,4,84,'04084','Word of Command','','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust an <b><i>Istari</i></b> character to search your deck for 1 card and add it to your hand. Shuffle your deck.','\"Picking up a faggot he held it aloft for a moment, and then with a word of command, naur an edraith ammen! he thrust the end of his staff into the midst of it. At once a great spout of green and blue flame sprang out, and the wood flared and sputtered.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9027','2016-03-12 15:32:36','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(176,12,3,4,85,'04085','Love of Tales','Condition.','Attach to a [lore] hero. Limit 1 per hero.\n<b>Response:</b> After a <b><i>Song</i></b> card is played, exhaust Love of Tales to add 1 resource to attached hero\'s resource pool.','\"I listened because I couldn\'t help myself, if you know what I mean. Lor bless me, sir, but I do love tales of that sort.\"\n<cite>Sam Gamgee, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801211c9019','2016-03-12 15:32:36','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(177,13,1,2,101,'04101','Glorfindel','Noldor. Noble. Warrior.','<b>Forced:</b> After Glorfindel exhausts to commit to a quest, raise your threat by 1.','Glorfindel was tall and straight; his hair was of shining gold, his face fair and young and fearless and full of joy; his eyes were bright and keen, and has voice like music; on his brow sat wisdom, and in his hand was strength.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,5,3,3,1,5,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9016','2016-03-12 15:36:22','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(178,13,2,3,102,'04102','Longbeard Elder','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After Longbeard Elder commits to a quest, look at the top card of the encounter deck. If that card is a location, place 1 progress token on the current quest. Otherwise, Longbeard Elder gets -1 [willpower] until the end of the phase.','',0,'3',NULL,2,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9021','2016-03-12 15:36:22','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(179,13,3,3,103,'04103','Path of Need','Condition.','Limit 1 per deck. Attach to a location.\nHeroes do not exhaust to attack, defend, or commit to a quest while attached location is the active location.','\"However it may prove, one must tread the path that need chooses!\"\n<cite>Gandalf, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,1,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9028','2016-03-12 15:36:23','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(180,13,2,1,104,'04104','Trollshaw Scout','Noldor. Scout.','Ranged.\nTrollshaw Scout does not exhaust to attack.\n<b>Forced:</b> After Trollshaw Scout attacks, either discard it from play or discard 1 card from your hand.','',0,'2',NULL,0,2,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9033','2016-03-12 15:36:24','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(181,13,4,1,105,'04105','Heavy Stroke','','<b>Response:</b> After a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> deals X damage to an enemy during combat, deal an additional X damage to that enemy. (Limit once per phase.)','\"Beside them Gimli stood with his stout legs apart, wielding his dwarf-axe.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9018','2016-03-12 15:36:24','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(182,13,2,2,106,'04106','Imladris Stargazer','Noldor.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Imladris Stargazer to choose a player. That player looks at the top 5 cards of his deck and then returns them to the top of his deck in any order.','',0,'2',NULL,0,0,1,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9019','2016-03-12 15:36:25','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(183,13,3,2,107,'04107','Light of Valinor','Condition.','Attach to a <b><i>Noldor</i></b> or <b><i>Silvan</i></b> hero.\nAttached hero does not exhaust to commit to a quest.','\"... those who have dwelt in the blassed realm live at once in both worlds, and against both the Seen and Unseen they have great power.\"\n<cite>Gandalf, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9020','2016-03-12 15:36:25','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(184,13,4,4,108,'04108','Daeron\'s Runes','','<b>Action:</b> Draw 2 cards. Then, discard 1 card from your hand.','\"These are Daeron\'s Runes, such as were used of old in Moria...\"\n<cite>Gandalf, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9010','2016-03-12 15:36:26','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(185,13,3,4,109,'04109','Healing Herbs','','Attach to a [lore] hero hero.\n<b>Action:</b> Discard Healing Herbs and exhaust attached hero to heal all damage on 1 character.','',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9017','2016-03-12 15:36:26','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(186,13,3,4,110,'04110','Asfaloth','Mount.','Attach to a <b><i>Noldor</i></b> or <b><i>Silvan</i></b> hero.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Asfaloth to place 1 progress token on any location. (2 tokens instead if attached hero is Glorfindel.)','Suddenly into view below came a white horse, gleaming in the shadows, running swiftly. In the dusk its headstall flickered and flashed as if it were studded with gems like living stars. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801212c9001','2016-03-12 15:36:27','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(187,14,1,4,128,'04128','Elrond','Noldor. Noble.','You may spend resources from Elrond\'s resource pool to pay for [spirit], [leadership], and [tactics] allies.\n<b>Response:</b> After a character is healed by another card effect, heal 1 damage on it.','\"But you do not stand alone.\"\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,13,3,2,3,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801213c9004','2016-03-12 15:40:24','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(188,14,4,3,129,'04129','We Are Not Idle',NULL,'<b>Action:</b> Exhaust X <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters to add X resources to a hero\'s resource pool and draw 1 card.','\"You should see the stone-paved roads of many colours! And the halls and cavernous streets under the earth with arches carved like trees; and the terraces and towers upon the Mountain\'s sides! Then you would see that we have not been idle.\" <cite>Glóin, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801213c9028','2016-03-12 15:40:25','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(189,14,3,3,130,'04130','Hardy Leadership','','Attach to a [leadership] hero.\nEach <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> gets +1 hit point.','\"We will seek the hidden door together. And we will come through. In the ruins of of the Dwarves, a dwarf\'s head will be less easy to bewilder than Elves or Men or Hobbits.\"\n<cite>Gandalf, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801213c9008','2016-03-12 15:40:25','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(190,14,4,1,131,'04131','Hands Upon the Bow','','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust a character you control with ranged to immediately declare it as an attacker (and resolve its attack) against an enemy in the staging area. It gets +1 [attack] during this attack.','\"We live now upon an island amid perils, and our hands are more often upon thr bowstring than upon the harp.\"\n<cite>Haldir, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-0801213c9007','2016-03-12 15:40:26','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(191,14,4,2,132,'04132','O Elbereth! Gilthonial!','',