l Custodian','Gondor.','Lower the cost to play Citadel Custodian by 1 for each <b><i>Gondor</i></b> ally in play.','',0,'5',NULL,1,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4823aae3-46ef-4a75-89f9-cbd3aa1b9010','2016-03-12 15:49:46','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(201,15,4,3,5,'05005','Mutual Accord','','<b>Action:</b> Until the end of the phase, each <b><i>Gondor</i></b> card in play gains the <b><i>Rohan</i></b> trait, and each Rohan card in play gains the Gondor trait.','\"These are the Rohirrim, as we name them, masters of horses... and have ever proved true to us, aiding us at need, and guarding our northern marches and the Gap of Rohan.\" <cite>Faramir, The Two Towers</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4823aae3-46ef-4a75-89f9-cbd3aa1b9060','2016-03-12 15:49:51','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(202,15,4,3,6,'05006','Wealth of Gondor','','<b>Action:</b> Choose a <b><i>Gondor</i></b> hero. Add 1 resource to that hero\'s resource pool.','Kings made tombs more splendid than houses of the living, and counted old names in the rolls of their descent dearer than the names of sons. <cite>The Two Towers</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4823aae3-46ef-4a75-89f9-cbd3aa1b9087','2016-03-12 15:49:54','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(203,15,2,1,7,'05007','Defender of Rammas','Gondor. Warrior.','','\"And the Enemy must pay dearly for the crossing of the River.\" <cite>Denethor, The Return of the King</cite>',0,'2',NULL,0,1,4,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4823aae3-46ef-4a75-89f9-cbd3aa1b9014','2016-03-12 15:49:57','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(204,15,4,1,8,'05008','Behind Strong Walls','','<b>Action:</b> Ready a defending <b><i>Gondor</i></b> character. That character gets +1 [defense] until the end of the phase.','...seven walls of stone so strong and old that it seemed to have been not builded by carven by giants out of the bones of the earth. <cite>The Return of the King</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4823aae3-46ef-4a75-89f9-cbd3aa1b9004','2016-03-12 15:5