fense]. (+2 [defense] instead if attached hero has the <b><i>Gondor</i></b> trait.)','There flowered a White Tree, and that was for Gondor...\n<cite>The Return of the King</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'09134509-191b-4903-b4b5-5e650f8143c1','2016-03-12 16:11:42','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(220,16,2,2,6,'06006','Ethir Swordsman','Outlands.','Each <b><i>Outlands</i></b> character you control gets +1 [willpower].','We heard of the horns in the hills ringing,\nthe swords shining in the South-kingdom.\n<cite>The Return of the King</cite>',0,'2',NULL,1,1,1,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'1c149f93-9e3b-42fa-878c-80b29563a283','2016-03-12 16:11:56','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(221,16,3,2,7,'06007','Ring of Barahir','Artifact. Item. Ring.','Attach to a hero.\nAttached hero gets +1 hit point for each <b><i>Artifact</i></b> attachment attached to it.\nIf attached hero is Aragorn, he also gains a [lore] resource icon.','',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'0ef9e385-b7e5-4676-a690-2dd8031aa8c8','2016-03-12 16:12:12','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(222,16,2,4,8,'06008','Anfalas Herdsman','Outlands.','Each <b><i>Outlands</i></b> character you control gets +1 hit point.','From the Anfalas, the Langstrand far away, a long line of men of many sorts, hunters and herdsmen and men of little villages... <cite>The Return of the King</cite>',0,'1',NULL,0,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'4cb4741d-c9d8-4d62-ab4f-50fa80c59fbb','2016-03-12 16:12:23','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(223,16,4,4,9,'06009','Mithrandir\'s Advice','','<b>Action:</b> Draw 1 card for each hero you control with a printed [lore] resource icon.','\"Let none now reject the counsels of Gandalf, whose long labours against Sauron come at last to their test.\" <cite>Aragorn, The Return of the King</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,NULL,'3c47d373-62bc-4321-9dc1-9b86b2046f68','2016-03-12 16:12:32','2016-03-17 23:47:22'),(224,16,4,5,10,'06010','A Good Harvest','','<b>Action:</b> Name a sphere. Until the end o